title: fastlane pilot export fails.
body:
### New Issue Checklist - [x] Updated fastlane to the latest version - [x] I read the [Contribution Guidelines](https://github.com/fastlane/fastlane/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md) - [x] I read [docs.fastlane.tools](https://docs.fastlane.tools) - [x] I searched for [existing GitHub issues](https://github.com/fastlane/fastlane/issues) ### Issue Description Running the latest fastlane update I now get an error when running the following command. This has been working perfectly for a long time: `fastlane pilot export -a com.my.app_id -c ~/Documents/export.csv` Looking for related GitHub issues on fastlane/fastlane... Found no similar issues.
